        "created_at": "2017-06-14T10:07:50.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I wrote a news piece on it the other day: <a href=\"http://www.decanter.com/wine/wine-regions/california/napa-valley/hail-storm-napa-valley-causes-damagede-370796/\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Freak hail storm hits Napa Valley vineyards - Decanter</a></p>\n<p>In brief, damage very patchy, most seemingly largely spared but a few folks hit hard.</p>",
