        "created_at": "2017-06-14T22:22:42.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Lee Braem\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n Lee Braem:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Merrill, I didn\u2019t know there was weather thread. I don\u2019t see it in the Index. Glad your vines ok.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=136083\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/original/3X/e/8/e87148ebcd1df56551c495d1105f732d10f7da42.png\" class=\"site-icon\" data-dominant-color=\"8C2626\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=136083\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"08:32PM - 02 January 2017\">WineBerserkers \u2013 2 Jan 17</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <img width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db3686/original/1X/973cca6246737ae55b5ad7fbc6bddc245f0ca306.png\" class=\"thumbnail onebox-avatar\">\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=136083\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">2017 West Coast Vintage Weather Thread</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Fine, Casey, then I\u2019ll start it\u2026  Snow here in So Hum, even down in Briceland at 600 ft.  Snowing now and has been off and on most of the day.  Looking forward to getting pruning done early this year, but not yet\u2026</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
